title: Treble one
creator_credit: Associated British-Pathe, John Robins and Peter Saunders
brief_description: A tribute to 111 Squadron, Royal Air Force, which until recently provided the RAF aerobatic team. Visiting the Squadron’s station in Suffolk, takes a brief look at the ground services - particularly radar equipment and safety procedures - then concentrates on flying sequences which end with some spectacular aerobatic scenes.
